1405
01:00:41.300 --> 01:00:42.734
slam!

1406
01:00:42.734 --> 01:00:44.367
You lose.

1407
01:00:44.367 --> 01:00:45.400
[grunts]

1408
01:00:45.400 --> 01:00:46.767
You lose.

1409
01:00:46.767 --> 01:00:49.900
