1515
01:06:09.567 --> 01:06:10.600
Yeah. I'm all right.
Doc.

1516
01:06:10.600 --> 01:06:11.967
Right here.
I'm all right.

1517
01:06:11.967 --> 01:06:13.467
They had me tied
to the bed. Kiley.

1518
01:06:13.467 --> 01:06:14.433
I tried to get out
of there.

1519
01:06:14.433 --> 01:06:16.500
But I was so drugged.
