There was Blake.

1523
01:06:22.667 --> 01:06:24.567
There was Kim.

1524
01:06:24.567 --> 01:06:27.066
There was--

1525
01:06:27.066 --> 01:06:28.600
I'm gonna make 'em
pay for this.

1526
01:06:28.600 --> 01:06:29.967
That's for damn sure.

1527
01:06:29.967 --> 01:06:32.300
They're gonna pay
for this.

1528
01:06:32.300 --> 01:06:34.166
Hey. Nick.
Blake's dead. right?
No.

1529
01:06:34.166 --> 01:06:36.433
