1544
01:06:59.133 --> 01:07:00.633
Yeah. I think so.
yeah. yeah. yeah.

1545
01:07:00.633 --> 01:07:03.367
All right.
well. I was in an empty pool.

1546
01:07:03.367 --> 01:07:05.567
I was--

1547
01:07:05.567 --> 01:07:08.734
All right. I'll get backup.
some forensics. all right?

1548
01:07:08.734 --> 01:07:09.734
